    "summary": "The user asks about the safety of taking Clarithromycin and Simvastatin together. The assistant correctly identifies a major drug-drug interaction but provides highly authoritative, clinically inaccurate advice by recommending the user immediately stop their maintenance medication and then provides unverified, arbitrary timelines for restarting it.",
